category: Python Virtual
requires: python39-stack-data
sdesc: "This is a library that extracts data from stack frames and tracebacks, particularly to display more useful tracebacks than the default. It powers the tracebacks in IPython and futurecoder."
ldesc: "The python3-stack-data virtual package. Selecting this package for installation will cause the python39-stack-data package to be installed."
external-source: python-stack-data

